<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Replica-Set on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/replica-set/</link><description>Recent content in Replica-Set on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/replica-set/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MongoDB OplogWindowTooSmall: oplog window exhausted</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/oplog-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/oplog-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when a secondary member in a replica set cannot keep up with the primary and falls out of the oplog window. The secondary must do a full initial sync to rejoin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write volume exceeds the secondary&amp;rsquo;s replication throughput&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oplog size is too small for the amount of write activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secondary hardware is underpowered (CPU, disk I/O)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network latency between primary and secondary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check current oplog window size:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printReplicationInfo&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// primary
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printSecondaryReplicationInfo&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// secondaries
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resize the oplog on the primary:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;runCommand&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;replSetResizeOplog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 16 GB
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor replication lag:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;members&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;forEach&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; lag: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;optimeDate&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;date&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; ms`&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upgrade secondary hardware or add more secondaries to distribute load.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;printSecondaryReplicationInfo&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// source: secondary1:27017
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// syncedTo: Thu Jul 16 2026 10:00:00 GMT+0000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 0 secs (0 hrs) behind the primary
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// source: secondary2:27017
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// syncedTo: Thu Jul 16 2026 09:00:00 GMT+0000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 3600 secs (1 hrs) behind the primary — likely will fall out of window
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/write-concern"&gt;MongoDB WriteConcernError&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>MongoDB WriteConcernError: not enough data-bearing nodes</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/write-concern/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/write-concern/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when a write operation specifies a write concern (e.g. &lt;code&gt;w: 3&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;w: &amp;quot;majority&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;) but not enough data-bearing replica set members are available to satisfy it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A replica set member has gone down or is lagging behind&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The write concern level is set higher than the number of healthy data-bearing nodes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network partition between the application and replica set members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Misconfigured write concern in connection options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check replica set status:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;rs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a more lenient write concern for non-critical writes:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }, { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;writeConcern&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; } })
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjust the connection string write concern:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;MongoClient&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;uri&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;writeConcern&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;majority&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;wtimeoutMS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add &lt;code&gt;wtimeout&lt;/code&gt; to avoid indefinite blocking:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;writeConcern&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;majority&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;wtimeout&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt; } }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Replicaset with 2 members, write concern w: 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }, { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;writeConcern&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; } })
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WriteConcernError: not enough data-bearing nodes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/duplicate-key"&gt;E11000 duplicate key error collection&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>